  "formatted_phone_number": "(02) 9374 4000",
  "website": "http://google.com/",
  "rating": 4.1,
  "reviews": [
    {
      "author_name": "Yashaswi Verma",
      "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105360031535707570077/reviews",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "en",
      "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUa8UHkSGjBSuHosbbG9N_y6Q0PbIDTaNS51t5AHyvVcNNWO0MYnQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2",
      "rating": 5,
      "relative_time_description": "3 weeks ago",
      "text": "Had a great time today. I went to the club and it had really great cocktails. The food was also really good. Overall, I had a great fun with my friends. The only problem was that the place is usually very crowded.",
      "time": 1755008960,
      "translated": false
    },
    {
      "author_name": "Simon Leaver",
      "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102334085932590158209/reviews",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "en",
      "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK9gELSUGQ_3FJlwnkhpOJlL-CHR_5kyGQK5wEF3cs-JAf8TA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo",
      "rating": 5,
      "relative_time_description": "4 months ago",
      "text": "Following a recent purchase this week, of a Vehicle from Lee of Prestige Trade Port Melbourne, I felt I should share my experience. Being in business for 28 years and a Reg. Practitioner with the VBA, Professionally I can not speak highly enough about Lee's professionalism and assistants from my initial enquiry, meeting, and my decision in purchasing the Vehicle that best suited my needs. Lee went out of his way to assist, disclose all my questions and further details about the Vehicle. To Lee's credit he accepted my txt msgs and questions on a Sunday afternoon. Nothing was a problem or an issue, which conveyed to me trust and confidence throughout the purchase.\nUpon pickup the Vehicle was immaculately presented with a full tank of fuel.\nI anticipate the same content and confidence will continue with the running of the Vehicle.\nI would certainly recommend Lee and Team, furthermore I will be doing further business in the future for my next purchase.\nKudos to you Lee, job well done.\nagain Thank you.\nSincerest Regards,\nSimon L.👌",
      "time": 1744930084,
      "translated": false
    },
    {
      "author_name": "Flo Yeow",
      "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101597484841229205770/reviews",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "en",
      "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUCED0nHINoONtoIhYrg_037nt9gzG8G4ZOxJ3RLinEhCioWYU8hrs=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba8",
      "rating": 5,
      "relative_time_description": "2 years ago",
      "text": "This is the Sales side of the couple of offices that Google has in Sydney. The engineering side is nicer but this is nice too.\n\nStraightforward set up, in a single column building, stairs and lift in the middle, and everything else around it. Professional baristas at The Press are really lovely people, and when I visited the dining hall was serving Carbonara on a cheese wheel. Make sure you stand at the rooftop balcony and enjoy the breeze and view of the surroundings.\n\nWith such gorgeous amenities and benefits, what's there not to like about working here.",
      "time": 1670547584,
      "translated": false
    },
    {
      "author_name": "Zyanya Avila Louis",
      "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104983763166583277550/reviews",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "en",
      "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWiqXZLmhx41ej7SvTJDg4EEO958R4siHNAOQI7JWIpbicllU5wjw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo",
      "rating": 5,
      "relative_time_description": "a month ago",
      "text": "would give Open Play infinity stars if I could. My daughter was born 2 months premature and had some mild delays in various areas of development. She qualified for speech, occupational, and physical therapy, so the San Diego Resource Center referred us to Open Play for the physical.\n\nWe were assigned Silvia DaFaria when Daughter was about 1 year old, and Silvia quickly became part of the family. She is so passionate about her work, and was just the person I needed when I was struggling with parenthood and feeling like the worst mom in the world (ya know, mom stuff). Daughter adores her, and I know it's because Silvia has a warmth and safety about her that any kid would respond to. I've laughed, cried, and lamented about life and parenthood with Silvia and could not have asked for a better person to help Daughter not only catch up on but SURPASS her gross motor milestones. Daughter turns 3 two days from when I am writing this review, and thanks to Silvia, she is doing things that are 6 months to a year ahead of her age group, even without adjusting her chronological age based on her prematurity. The progress has been stunning, and I'm honored to have seen Silvia at work. She has genuinely changed our lives for the better. Daughter, is capable, confident, and strong, and I couldn't be more grateful for the early intervention resources from the SDRC and Open Play.",
      "time": 1754082390,
      "translated": false
    },
    {
      "author_name": "Jb Jb",
      "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102424035579149536340/reviews",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "en",
      "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL2S7hmOhf06m9Itwm2VbHvUfxbYU02hu2Ba6e63T-Ld9vq5A=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2",
      "rating": 1,
      "relative_time_description": "a month ago",
      "text": "Horrible team whomever reviewed business profile appeals. Reject and don’t read any information supplied. Finding where to re-appeal has wasted so much time for something so straight forward. Let alone finding a contact us.",
      "time": 1753452024,
